[resource]
script = ExtResource("1_y1hes")
release_version = "v1.3.3 (CM37E)"
notes = "[TITLE]Proxies
Added two new proxies: Stockholder and Cross Seller.
  These two are meant to be replacements for the now-removed Cash Cow and Live Wire.
Added three new proxy effects: Undercutter, Creditor, and Copycat
[TITLE]Balance Changes
A couple changes were made to make Endless Mode a bit harder.
  Reduced the Room Count cap from 29 to 25
  Increased cog damage by a tiny smidge. (Approx. 3-15% Higher)
  Administrator health multiplier will now scale every five floors. Now they'll (mostly) have more HP than proxies!
On top of that, a few overpowered items were nerfed.
  Bee Wings: 50% of Base Speed -> 25% of Base Speed
  Rainbow Jellybean: Now scales additively (2, 3, 4, etc.) instead of multiplicatively (2, 4, 8, etc.)
  Dragon Wings: 5 Jellybeans per 1% boost -> 10 Jellybeans per 1% boost
  Roman Helmet: Four Stars/Q4 -> Four Stars/Q5
  Dragon Wings and Roman Helmet were removed from the Golden Chest pool.
  Roman Helmet was added to the Special Chest pool.
[TITLE]Other
Properly applied a few missing commits from the project. Sorry about that!
  Because of this, the Cash Cow, Live Wire, and a few credits were removed.
Hotfixes for 1.3.0 and onward have been properly added.
Patch notes for 1.3.1 and onward have been formatted correctly, too.
Added seven new secret seeds. If you want to try them out, then here is the list:
  'fog', 'sad', 'neigh', 'jellybeans', 'solicitor', '1987', 'help'
[TITLE]Hotfix #1
Adjusted an aspect of the 'jellybeans' seed.
[TITLE]Hotfix #2
Did a second adjustment of the directors' health formula for more extreme scaling.
[TITLE]Hotfix #3
Boss Health Scaling was adjusted and now properly works."
metadata/_custom_type_script = "uid://d1j0hh6tsgy0r"
